txt.en: Vâr Nuchur can be found west of Maergrind.\n\nYou should explore Vâr Nuchur for Varthmath.
You have successfully defeated gredbyg and collected grodbog hive samples for Varthmath. You should meet with Varthmath at Asbaj-khîrfin once you have completed your tasks.
Vâr Nuchur can be found west of Maergrind.\n\nYou should defeat gredbyg and collect samples from the hive.
Gredbyg buzz and swarm around the old mirror gardens
'One of the grodbog hives that I wish to explore is the old gardens, called Vâr Nuchur. While you are there, could you collect some samples of their hive? I would like to study its properties.'
Varthmath seeks to learn more about the grodbog presence in Máttugard.
Defeated gredbyg and collected grodbog hive samples.
